{"tid":307100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中印邊境衝突,印度學者倡用「核彈」對付中國","createTime":"2017-07-03T05:38:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-03T15:19:02.000Z","uid":41351,"like":68,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6c13d9c228dd3dc2a9fbc77e53f4445e1f47b028","tid":307100,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T05:38:12.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中印邊境緊張喧囂塵上，近年來佔領了印度至少2000多平方公里的國土，也傳出解放軍將在中印邊境部屬坦克。而印度的戰略研究所教授近日語出驚人，認為應該在邊境部屬核彈頭洲際飛彈，才能真正阻遏中國在中印邊境的狼虎掠奪野心。<br />\n<br />\n據《印度斯坦時報》報導，新德里政策研究中心戰略研究所教授加雷尼（Brahma Chellaney）發表一篇專文，名為「貿易戰/印度對中國發動最強大武器的時刻降臨」（It&rsquo;s time India used its most powerful weapon against China:&thinsp;Trade），專文指出，中國近年侵占印度近2000平方公里的國土，印度卻允許中國每年高達600億美元（約1.8兆新台幣）的出超額，這種做法只會讓中國得寸進尺。<br />\n<br />\n文中更直接指出，印度在本質上是針對中國的。並表示印度必須加強邊界防禦，提高其核導彈和導彈威懾能力，例如部屬長程巡弋飛彈或是能投遞多枚核彈頭的洲際導彈，以阻止中國的「狼性」掠奪。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2119313\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2119313&d=cIbmEudI4lsiCKtkGVUrqkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=c5034be9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2119313&h=6d86979f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2119313</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.read01.com/uploads/0FYGAmnXnG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.read01.com%2Fuploads%2F0FYGAmnXnG.jpg&h=414c7c20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i1.wp.com/inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_match/0/416266219/0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Finews.gtimg.com%2Fnewsapp_match%2F0%2F416266219%2F0&h=9c1c5208&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a0ea7197d66934437bcb4588718dc934916c15d","tid":307100,"uid":9104,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T05:46:24.000Z","msg":"呢兩個開波 全球少廿億人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03416ad0118e7